OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy start with a
OL,6,Ffew showers around. These will soon
OL,7,Fclear to leave a dry morning with
OL,8,Fsunny spells developing. Cloud
OL,9,Fincreasing in the afternoon to bring
OL,10,Fthe odd light shower but most places
OL,11,Fstaying dry.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA largely dry evening with
OL,14,Fsome late brightness. Mainly dry with
OL,15,Fclear spells overnight but some
OL,16,Fshowers will affect East Lothian and
OL,17,Fthe Borders later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
