OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA mostly dry and sunny
OL,6,Fmorning in the west. Cloudier with
OL,7,Fshowers over the Borders and the east
OL,8,Fand some of these showers will spread
OL,9,Finto the west during afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Ftouch of frost early Wednesday then
OL,13,Fmainly dry and bright, but showers
OL,14,Farriving later. Showers or longer
OL,15,Fspells of rain on Thursday and Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
